data.value: Please, select a date before today.

data.name: contabil_quick_guide1
data.value: When checked, this option enables the feature to select from the grid several contracts for processing cash flow, financial statement, accounting statement, contract termination or renegotiation of fees.

data.name: contabil_quick_guide2
data.value: This form lists the contracts covered by IFRS16. Use the filters (funnel) to manipulate the sample data. Click on the column title to sort the data in ascending ↑ or descending ↓ order. Double-click on the grid line to select the contract for which you want to consult or process the cash flow, financial statement or accounting statement.

data.name: contabil_quick_guide3
data.value: Select which action you want to perform on the selected contract: cash flow, financial statement, accounting statement, contract termination or renegotiation of fees. Then choose the applicable scenario, which can be REAL, NOMINAL, INFLATED, CURRENCY and USGAAP. These scenarios are parameterized in the system according to the use license agreement signed with NESTA.

data.name: contabil_quick_guide4
data.value: After selecting the contract and the respective applicable scenario, click on the PROCESS button to execute the cash flow, financial statement, accounting statement, contract termination or renegotiation of fees. When present, the processes are executed simultaneously in the REAL, NOMINAL and INFLATED scenarios. Specifically for the financial statement, when the deadline is not noted, the statement is executed until the end of the contract term. Specifically for the accounting statement, when the deadline is not noted, the accounting is carried out until the last entry recorded on the financial statement.

data.name: contabil_quick_guide5
data.value: Right-click on the grid to export the data collection in CSV ("Comma-Separated-Values" formats supported by Microsoft Excel, Google Sheets, Apple Numbers, OpenOffice Calc, LibreOffice) or XLSX (Microsoft Excel) . Choose the Refresh option to show in the grid the latest version of the data collection recorded in the database.

data.name: contabil_quick_guide6
data.value: This form lists the contracts covered by IFRS16. Use the filters (funnel) to manipulate the sample data. Click on the column title to sort the data in ascending ↑ or descending ↓ order. Double-click on the grid line to select the contract for which you want to consult or process the cash flow, financial statement or accounting statement.

data.name: contabil_quick_guide7
data.value: When selecting the contract, the fields will be filled with the information from the Contract Code, the Index used in the contract, the Contract Description used for classification and the Supplier associated with the Contract.

data.name: contabil_quick_guide8
data.value: Choose the scenario on which you want to view the selected contract cash flow, financial statement or accounting statement. The scenarios can be REAL (contract currency), NOMINAL, INFLATION, CURRENCY (functional currency) and USGAAP. These scenarios are parameterized in the system according to the license agreement signed with NESTA.
